(firstQuint)A Control Study to Evaluate The Efficacy And Safety of Ozone-therapy in Chronic Hepatitis B.

 Total of 439 patients with chronic hepatitis B were divided according to patients' intention into two arms.

 173 patients in arm I were treated with medical ozone therapy with humares which was made in Germany for at least 12 weeks.

266 patients in arm II were treated with conventional interferon- for at least 24 weeks.

Patients in both groups were followed-up for 24 weeks.

Virology response, biochemistry response and hepatitis B viral serological response will be studied at 12 weeks after the treatment, at the end of treatment and after 24 weeks of follow-up.

